{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&#xA0;</div></div>", "i": 6444174}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Por resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xBA; 2.044, de 21 de agosto de 2003, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, autor&#xED;zase a PESQUERA QUINTERO UNO S.A. para realizar actividades extractivas en aguas internacionales con la nave &quot;Do&#xF1;a Mar&#xED;a&quot;, cuyas caracter&#xED;sticas n&#xE1;uticas son las siguientes:</div><br><br><div class=\"p\">Matr&#xED;cula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2668</div><div class=\"p\">Se&#xF1;al distintiva&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; CB-4219</div><div class=\"p\">Eslora de arqueo&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 46,76 m</div><div class=\"p\">Manga&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  11,00 m</div><div class=\"p\">Puntal&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  5,40 m</div><div class=\"p\">T.R.G. (Internacional)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  1017,36 m3</div><div class=\"p\">Capacidad de bodega&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1136,46 m3</div><div class=\"p\">Potencia motor principal&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  2250,00 Hp</div><div class=\"p\">Potencia motores auxiliares&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1777,00 Hp</div><br></div>", "i": 6444175}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Valpara&#xED;so, 21 de agosto de 2003.- Felipe Sandoval Precht, Subsecretario de Pesca.</div><br></div>", "i": 6444176}], "proyectos": [], "otrosSistemas": [], "jurisprudencia": [], "doctrina": [], "metadatos": {"tiene_notas": false, "tipos_numeros": [{"tipo": "3", "numero": "2044", "abreviacion": "RES", "descripcion": "Resolucion", "compuesto": "RES-2044"}], "organismos": ["MINISTERIO DE ECONOMÍA", "FOMENTO Y RECONSTRUCCION", "SUBSECRETARÍA DE PESCA"], "titulo_nor